=== How to get started ===

This is a project to reproduce the bug http://java.net/jira/browse/JAVASERVERFACES-1975.

Just issue "mvn" and maven does the rest;

Once up, point your browser to "http://localhost:8080/bug3/test.html" and you will see the problem.
To see the working example, point your browser to "http://localhost:8080/bug3/test2.html".